{"tid":1243912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發現左樣應該幾有用既前線裝備！","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:47:37.000Z","uid":61830,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9985004ee190419a0555efc13467c17d0de76f7f","tid":1243912,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"今日去行街買小小洗車用品<br />\n比我發現左呢樣野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juVhrbq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuVhrbq.jpg&h=750dcbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手動打氣既噴壺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n容量：1.8L<br />\n射程：3-5米<br />\n噴射形狀：直射/扇形<br />\n唔講咁多，睇示範<br />\n<a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/RKGbZU5Ubd2FVgQoYB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fgifs%2FRKGbZU5Ubd2FVgQoYB&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=2011ede0\" target=\"_blank\">https://giphy.com/gifs/RKGbZU5Ubd2FVgQoYB</a><br />\n<br />\n直射適合：畫家painting<br />\n扇形適合：食完pepper lunch整污糟後快速有效沖洗面部/手部，建議後排/first aid用。<br />\n<br />\n價錢$168, 雖然有d貴，但值得犧牲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二樣<br />\n平價電單車手套<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKZiaHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKZiaHc.jpg&h=b31da50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防水 <strong>波子骨有甲</strong><br />\n價錢：$128<br />\n揸得電單車有返對手套係好重要<br />\n同一般勞工手套差好遠<br />\n雖然呢對唔係最好，但平又點都好過無<br />\n<br />\n以上兩樣都係深水埗深之都1樓某汽車用品店搵到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n如果budget多小小建議去真正電單車買手套<br />\n<strong>要買指骨、手背有鐵既手套</strong><br />\n價錢：300-500不等<br />\n有朋友去揸電單車唔小心比野扑到手背腫哂成隻雞蛋咁<br />\n保護雙手真係好重要！一傷就失去行動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他裝備好多post有講，我唔多講啦。<br />\n各位加油"},{"pid":"f1ef0d3e6f2c8755186f70da91f1a18fecf65608","tid":1243912,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f87d0bd10946a250e6dcdf68ae454ed12d100d4","tid":1243912,"uid":263522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7352055067ee8bcf5c93754eaae8ba29b326367b","tid":1243912,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外深水埗仲有d鋪頭有賣防滅蟲毒藥既口罩，可以送便買埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"81b7663094f0854822cdbd3c04ba1cc052fc4e69","tid":1243912,"uid":61830,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再補充多樣深水埗西九對面有間叫利x/x力既電單車用品店，有需要真係要去睇睇有咩岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某d台灣牌子既開面帽幾百有</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好買full face電單車頭盔<br />\n一黎熱死自己<br />\n二黎戴唔到豬嘴去滅蟲</span>"},{"pid":"53b6c8ff4c986f42310311c6ddf945a75ee13751","tid":1243912,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cfcd0c56d9744d96e8cb001d5e0cb59cf0c14152","tid":1243912,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"439dd1401f249cbc0067974eb4de1c047ce76920","tid":1243912,"uid":260914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"推俾大家"},{"pid":"706162d146674cd289abc13adff5e7dcf8742559","tid":1243912,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:23:56.000Z","msg":"good wor！"},{"pid":"73054d9263e8698b6fe74ea1871023adaa6ac69d","tid":1243912,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a68900a23c9387479596a1c6e81a7a47fe0484fc","tid":1243912,"uid":199845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T19:12:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c80f676a170768b6a6953da4f6b288b0879849cf","tid":1243912,"uid":2422